West Africans Fleeing to Niger From Libya Top 57,000

-- B y   D j i b r i l   S a i d o u
-- 
2011-04-27T06:36:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/west-africans-fleeing-to-libya-from-niger-top-57-000-migration-body-says.html
(Corrects to say refugees fled to Niger in first
paragraph.)  More than 57,000 west Africans have
fled to Niger from  Libya  since February because of violence,
Abibatou Wane, director of the  International Organization  for
Migration, said on Niamey-based Radio Anfani.  The refugees include 54,000 Nigeriens and 3,200 nationals
of other countries in West Africa, she said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Tim Smith  in Sydney at 
 tsmith58@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
